	<h1 class="title">这些卖汉堡、炸鸡、抱枕和汽水的公司，走场时装秀也是不容易啊！</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/26306/small/26306.jpg?1461683679" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">宣海伦 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-11-20 17:07:06 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/17600/medium/17600.jpg?1447627585" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="17600" data-title="《这些卖汉堡、炸鸡、抱枕和汽水的公司，走场时装秀也是不容易啊！》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/17600/medium/17600.jpg?1447627585" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/17600.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
